address.streetAddress: Grandin Plan, Justify at Triple Crown

location.fullValue: Grandin Plan, Justify at Triple Crown

data.description: Gorgeous 3,000+ sf, 4 bed/3.5 in the heart of Triple Crown - the Morris by Fischer Homes has it all! The large chef's kitchen features an oversized island, stainless steel appliances, and double ovens.  Tasteful, updated decor throughout includes accent walls, shiplap, window cornices, and much more.  *NEW* LVP throughout entire 1st floor ties all the spaces together.  The custom office has dual built in work-spaces - perfect for WFH professionals and students alike.  The massive primary bedroom boasts transom windows, a large en-suite with shower and soaking tub and a custom built-in closet with drawers.  The 4th bedroom has its own attached bath, comfortable for houseguests or the in-laws.  The backyard is HUGE, flat and fenced with plenty of room to play.  The massive 16x32 covered patio is the perfect outdoor oasis to watch the game or unwind in the hot tub.  The western craftsman elevation features a covered patio, accent corbels, and hipped-roof angles.  Tinted rear windows, a whole home humidifier and energy efficient electric appliances round out awesome list of amenities.  *Agents - see remarks*
